data.description: A Place to Call Home-This beautiful, meticulously cared for home was the original model. It has 4 Bedroom and 3 Bathrooms located on a corner lot in well established neighborhood.  Entering this spacious home you will find high ceilings, tiled entry, a study/library, formal dining with custom trim, bright open updated Kitchen with granite countertops and wooden cabinetry, Elegant Appliances; Kitchen sink has reverse osmosis system; Freshly painted Breakfast Area, Large Living Room with fireplace ;Built-in entertainment center, Primary Bedroom has plantation shutters, Primary Bathroom has tile, jacuzzi tub, double sink and large walk-in closet,  Half-Bath has shower; Second floor has a huge Game Room, three Bedrooms with large closets, Bathrooms are bright with tub/shower; Ceiling fans throughout; Other features include Recently Replaced Roof-2021, Finished Garage, Patio Area, Huge Backyard with Mature Trees; And Much More! Near to shopping and schools; Easy Access to I-45; A Must See!
